  "text": "These data provide evidence of the unique properties of WCRs that can be exploited experimentally. However, the WCR advantage lies not only in high-resolution recordings, but also in the opportunity to manipulate systematically the intracellular milieu [CITATION_1] . Thus, in the present study, we were able to test our hypotheses and manipulate ionic fluxes that contribute to V, fluctuations.",
